Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:41.11,Default0,,0,0,0,,怎麽啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:48.09,Default0,,0,0,0,,亲爱的~姐姐 亲启
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:50.66,Default0,,0,0,0,,姐~姐，还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.96,Default0,,0,0,0,,开始想日本了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,你出国之后我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:02.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,还是一样有精神\N（长女 葵司）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:06.81,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们姐妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:09.01,Default0,,0,0,0,,会一起做家务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:14.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,快来帮忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:24.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:25.89,Default0,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:29.93,Default0,,0,0,0,,次女 最能干的咲 \N五女 帮忙做家务的娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,你也来帮忙啦\N等我吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.33,Default0,,0,0,0,,你也来帮忙啦\N等我吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,三女 以声优为目标的小南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:43.14,Default0,,0,0,0,,饭前别吃糖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:45.35,Default0,,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,葵还不是没帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,我等等就帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:02.23,Default0,,0,0,0,,我可是很忙呢\N（四女：向往名媛的葵）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:11.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,好 帽子脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.14,Default0,,0,0,0,,别玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:12.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,别玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.18,Default0,,0,0,0,,六女：外号“社长”的有纱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:19.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,我才没有在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.31,Default0,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.78,Default0,,0,0,0,,我是要当偶像的昵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:28.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,七女：追星的高中生 萌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.63,Default0,,0,0,0,,好啦 快吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.46,Default0,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:42.24,Default0,,0,0,0,,好香唷 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:48.48,Default0,,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:52.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:57.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,你不可以一直吃零嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.12,Default0,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:03.89,Default0,,0,0,0,,吃饭前不可以吃\N我有吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:08.30,Default0,,0,0,0,,为啥她比较多\N好诈唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.23,Default0,,0,0,0,,什麽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:16.00,Default0,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:27.75,Default0,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.58,Default0,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.89,Default0,,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:36.19,Default0,,0,0,0,,姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:40.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,我们想説 司姐差不多要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,就写了这封信给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:49.04,Default0,,0,0,0,,其实我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.87,Default0,,0,0,0,,突然来了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:54.54,Default0,,0,0,0,,是我们都不认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.54,Default0,,0,0,0,,男人唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:06.65,Default0,,0,0,0,,跟七姐妹同居的后宫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:13.99,Default0,,0,0,0,,抱歉我一直没告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:19.13,Default0,,0,0,0,,你其实有没有血缘关系的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:25.01,Default0,,0,0,0,,我死后就拿信到这个地方来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:29.41,Default0,,0,0,0,,她们会照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:34.55,Default0,,0,0,0,,那是你妈妈跟你的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:39.69,Default0,,0,0,0,,妈妈是緑 长女是司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:43.72,Default0,,0,0,0,,次女是咲 后面还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:48.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,好好活下去唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.80,Default0,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:56.57,Default0,,0,0,0,,可是妈妈去世很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:05:01.34,Default0,,0,0,0,,只有我们住这了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:05.38,Default0,,0,0,0,,不过一起住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:09.05,Default0,,0,0,0,,对啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:13.09,Default0,,0,0,0,,好开心唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.92,Default0,,0,0,0,,我是小咲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.59,Default0,,0,0,0,,我是小南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.63,Default0,,0,0,0,,我是娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.20,Default0,,0,0,0,,我是小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.97,Default0,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:34.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,好好自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.58,Default0,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.61,Default0,,0,0,0,,我是有纱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:45.02,Default0,,0,0,0,,我是小萌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:49.42,Default0,,0,0,0,,好期待哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:53.09,Default0,,0,0,0,,好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:57.13,Default0,,0,0,0,,房间怎麽办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.53,Default0,,0,0,0,,还有个房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.37,Default0,,0,0,0,,就那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.21,Default0,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:11.08,Default0,,0,0,0,,先打扫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:15.12,Default0,,0,0,0,,等饭吃饱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.32,Default0,,0,0,0,,那我们先去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.15,Default0,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.35,Default0,,0,0,0,,吃完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:25.02,Default0,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:29.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.90,Default0,,0,0,0,,吃完再説
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:33.10,Default0,,0,0,0,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.14,Default0,,0,0,0,,又剩下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:42.28,Default0,,0,0,0,,那这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:46.31,Default0,,0,0,0,,你们吃完的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.15,Default0,,0,0,0,,有奖励哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.92,Default0,,0,0,0,,真的？\N可以吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:57.32,Default0,,0,0,0,,快吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:06.50,Default0,,0,0,0,,好好吃唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:15.68,Default0,,0,0,0,,吃完啦 那麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.51,Default0,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:22.65,Default0,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.52,Default0,,0,0,0,,摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:38.06,Default0,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:42.84,Default0,,0,0,0,,我可是做菜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.71,Default0,,0,0,0,,摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:12.20,Default0,,0,0,0,,好棒\N摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:17.70,Default0,,0,0,0,,好诈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:35.69,Default0,,0,0,0,,直接摸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.88,Default0,,0,0,0,,再摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.09,Default0,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
